Life has been on the move and here is a little glimpse of my days! I have been working with amazing humans and constantly being pushed everyday to be better for them all! It’s crazy to think this is my actual job! I have been so blessed in my life to be around this amazing game and I wouldn’t trade it for the world! 

Check out my new website 🤩 link in bio!

It has been hard to keep up with social media lately but in honor of @auprosoftball starting tonight on @espn there is no better way then making a post about @nniiiss! There have been some big changes in life this past year and this beautiful soul has been by my side every step of the way!! Her calm presence makes my world a better place 🥰

It’s been amazing to watch @nniiiss continue to take her training and self to new levels. When you don’t have someone to train with it’s easy to just take the day off, but she always stuck to her plan. I can’t wait to see all her discipline and commitment pay off this season!! 

Pitchers watch out 👀 and hitters I would avoid hitting it to short if I were you!! 

Beyond proud of you Niss! I love you 😘💛
